ZH: 我的房间墙上有一个小缝隙。
EN: There is a small crack on the wall of my room.
ZH: 她从墙的缝隙中偷偷地看着。
EN: She peered surreptitiously through the crack in the wall.
ZH: 屋顶上的瓦片之间有一些缝隙。
EN: There are some gaps between the tiles on the roof.
ZH: 我们需要填补这些墙壁的缝隙。
EN: We need to fill up these wall crevices.
ZH: 在这个岩石缝隙中能看到水流。
EN: Water flows in this rock crevice.
ZH: 这道墙的缝隙中有些灰尘。
EN: There is some dust in the gap of the wall.
ZH: 他在缝隙中藏起了一把钥匙。
EN: He hid a key in the crevice.
ZH: 雨从破碎的屋顶缝隙中滴下来。
EN: Rain dripped from the cracks in the broken roof.
ZH: 这扇门的缝隙太大，风能吹进来。
EN: The gap in this door is too wide, the wind can come in.
ZH: 我从窗口的缝隙中看到一只小鸟。
EN: I saw a little bird through the crack in the window.
