EN: My phone fell into the crevice in the corner of the wall.
ZH: 这个箱子的缝隙太大，里面的东西会掉出来。
EN: The gaps in this box are too large, things inside will fall out.
ZH: 这扇窗户的缝隙让屋内透风。
EN: The gaps in this window allow ventilation in the room.
